Trinity::

She smiled at Windlord. "Oh yeah, I'm tough alright."
She giggled when Aerotaur said that she could ride on his 
back."Alright."

She jumped and growled as the ship fell. She took a step towards the 
bot that was waving at them.  She growled and ran towards the bot. 
She stopped and stood about 3 yards away from the bot. 
She growled in her kitten growl,"Who are you? And what are you doing 
here."  She stopped growling and looked up at the bot. "Don't worry, 
I won't hurt you, as long as you don't hurt my friends."
